2.4 Integer Values
==================

Integers must consist only of digits, and may have an optional leading
sign character (`+' or `-').


File: libconfig.info,  Node: Floating Point Values,  Next: Boolean Values,  Prev: Integer Values,  Up: Configuration Files

2.5 Floating Point Values
=========================

Floating point values must consist only of digits, one decimal point, an
optional leading sign character (`+' or `-'), and an optional exponent.


